<p>The Calgary Flames began playing in the National Hockey League in 1972 and currently play at Scotiabank Saddledome.

	
		They have won the Stanley Cup once.
	

  
    The Calgary Flames have appeared in the Stanley Cup Finals 3 times.
  

  
    They have won 7 division titles.
  


	
		The team was previously the Atlanta Flames but moved in 1980.
	
